description: Horns N Snouts is a Barbecue Truck bringing delicious meats to the greater Dallas area. A recent winner of the NorthWood Church Food truck Competition, Horns N Snouts brings the flavor with BBQ pulled pork and brisket, served as a sandwich or by it's self and priced by the pound. In addition to their BBQ goodness, Horns N Snouts has amazing sides and fries done in their signature style. "Life, Liberty, and BBQ for All!"
name: Horns N Snouts
